$PROBLEM ZERBAXA
$INPUT ID NUM TIME DV AMT RATE ADDL II CMT MDV EVID HEIGHT BW SEX AGE SOFA PCT ECMO CRRT ELWI CI CRE ALB PROTEIN
$DATA ..\..\..\..\data\derived\RawData.csv IGNORE=I
$SUBROUTINE ADVAN5 TRANS1
$MODEL COMP=(DEPOT1) ;1-CEFTOLOZANE CENTR COMP=(PER1) ;2-CEFTOLOZANE PERIPH COMP=(DEPOT2) ;3-TAZOBACTAM CENTR COMP=(PER2) ;4-TAZOBACTAM PERIPH $PK
BSA = 0.20247*(HEIGHT/100)**0.725*BW**0.425 ;(DuBois & DuBois) CLCR = (140-AGE)*BW/72/CRE*0.85**(SEX) ;(Cockcroft-Gault formula) CO = CI*BSA;
V1C = THETA(1)*EXP(ETA(1)) CLC = THETA(2)*EXP(ETA(2)) V2C = THETA(3)*EXP(ETA(3)) QC = THETA(4)*EXP(ETA(4)) V1T = THETA(5)*EXP(ETA(5)) CLT = THETA(6)*EXP(ETA(6)) V2T = THETA(7)*EXP(ETA(7)) QT = THETA(8)*EXP(ETA(8))
K10 = CLC/V1C K12 = QC/V1C K21 = QC/V2C K30 = CLT/V1T K34 = QT/V1T K43 = QT/V2T
$ERROR IF(CMT.EQ.1) THEN IPRED=A(1)/V1C Y=IPRED*(1+EPS(1)) ENDIF IF(CMT.EQ.3) THEN IPRED=A(3)/V1T Y=IPRED*(1+EPS(2)) ENDIF
$THETA (0, 30.2) ;THETA1 V1C [L] (0, 6.28) ;THETA2 CLC [L/h] (0, 55.4) ;THETA3 V2C [L] (0, 5.9) ;THETA4 QC [L/h] (0, 50) ;THETA5 V1T [L] (0, 16.8) ;THETA6 CLT [L/h] (0, 3) ;THETA7 V2T [L] (0, 20) ;THETA8 QT [L/h]
$OMEGA 0 FIX ;11 ETA-V1C 0.1 ;22 ETA-CLC 0 FIX ;33 ETA-V2C 0 FIX ;44 ETA-QC
$OMEGA 0.2 ;55 ETA-V1T 0.2 ;66 ETA-CLT
$OMEGA 0 FIX ;77 ETA-V2T 0 FIX ;88 ETA-QT
;--------SIGMAS $SIGMA 0.2 ; 11 PROPC, % $SIGMA 0.2 ; 22 PROPT, %
$ESTIMATION METHOD=1 INTER NOABORT MAXEVAL=9990 NSIG=3 SIGL=9 PRINT=2 $COV
$TABLE ID NUM TIME MDV IPRED CWRES EVID CMT NPDE NOPRINT ONEHEADER FILE=SDTAB.DAT
$TABLE ID NUM V1C CLC V1T CLT ETA2 ETA5 ETA6 NOAPPEND NOPRINT ONEHEADER FILE=PATAB.DAT
$TABLE ID NUM HEIGHT CLCR BW AGE SOFA PCT CRRT ELWI CI CRE ALB PROTEIN CO BSA NOAPPEND NOPRINT ONEHEADER FILE=COTAB.DAT
$TABLE ID NUM SEX ECMO NOAPPEND NOPRINT ONEHEADER FILE=CATAB.DAT
